## Maintenance rules

- **Each entry MUST cite a source** — either `archive/<task-id>.md` (link to the task brief that produced it) or `manual` (added by hand without a task).
- **Re-curate at least quarterly.** Update the `last-curated` date at the top. Use `harness curate-memory` for guided cleanup.
- **Hard size limit ~200 lines.** When approaching the limit, consolidate similar entries or promote stable conventions into [{{paths_architecture_doc}}](../{{paths_architecture_doc}}) and remove from here.
- **No stale entries.** If an entry refers to code that no longer exists, delete it.
- **Categories are fixed**: Conventions / Pitfalls / Decisions / Open questions. Don't invent new categories.
